snippet.title: Itsy Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Hi I'm otter and my first solo indie game, Itsy, releases on Steam today!   Itsy is a heart tug the length of a bus ride. A narrative climb up the waterspout about the struggles of Autism burnout.
